[span8]
Stefano Greek Italian Restaurant located in Temple Terrace has been serving Greek, Italian and American food since 1994.
Stefano Greek Italian Restaurant – 8600 N56st Street, Temple Terrace
We are proud to offer a wide variety in our menu. When you are in Temple Terrace stop by and try one of our famous Greek Salads, Gyro wraps, Moussaka, Dolmades, Chicken Parm, Chicken Alfredo, Lasagna and much more. Click here to view our menu.
All of our menu items are made with fresh market ingredients.
Stefano Greek Italian Restaurant has been voted BEST GREEK restaurant in Tampa Northeast, Temple Terrace for more than eight years and our Greek salad has been rated number one Greek Salad in Tampa by the Tampa Tribune.
We are open 7 days a week serving breakfast (wed-sun), lunch and dinner.
